reviewText: I love john f kennedy and his brother Robert f kennedy on dvd thank you amazon

This is an early history of JFK and the multiple medical problems that he over came.  It is not a history of "13 days in October".  I thought this would give me a better view of how JFK was able to muster the amazing courage he displayed in October of 1962.  This gives a glimpse into his toughness but not what I was looking for.
